element_texts.text:
198 Hamilton St
New Haven, Conn.
April 28/[19]31
Dear Dr. Taylor,
May I join your host of friends and send my greetings on your birthday—the one which rounds out four score years! I presume you will be having dinner at the Commons. I can, in imagination, see you at...

element_texts.text:
...the head of the center table, flowers and candles and a birthday cake, and the happy chatter of the family.
Accept my sincere good wishes, and may you live many more years to bless and help humanity.
Sincerely yours—
Anne M. MacDonald.
